==English==
===Noun Phrase===
'''nervous system'''

# {{anatomy}} The system which coordinates the activity of the muscles, monitors the organs, constructs and processes input from the senses, and initiates actions. In [[vertebrate]]s it consists of the [[brain]], the [[brainstem]], the [[spinal cord]], [[nerve]]s, and [[ganglion|ganglia]].

